patthana17.19:0.2_0: (This should be expanded as in the teachings.)
patthana17.19:0.3_0: he deposited himself with the following.
patthana17.19:1.1_0: skilled in the ear ... the nose ... tongue ... body ...
patthana17.19:2.1_0: So they don’t clearly see the reason for speaking to the teaching.
patthana17.19:3.1_0: The skillful is not the supported by the skillful, and the support that arises conditioned by the support.
patthana17.19:4.1_0: One’s skillful and unskillful phenomena don’t arise because of.
